WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
ظآزMemories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreamsظآز

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
ظآزOnly by moving forward
can you find reunionظآز

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
ظآزEndings only mark new routesظآز

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
ظآزIt's all part of the sceneryظآز

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
ظآزTo the horizon's callظآز

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
ظآزYour journey hasn't startedظآز

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
ظآزLet time embrace you
and wash away the pastظآز

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
ظآزPut every twist behind youظآز

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
ظآزDrift leisurely through timeظآز

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
ظآزMake headway against the windظآز

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
ظآزLet mountains bow to your paceظآز

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
ظآزRush towards a life without regretظآز

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:34.960 --> 01:37.644
=Episode 23=

01:38.544 --> 01:39.145
What is this?

01:39.744 --> 01:43.104
Her Highness discovered this item
while organizing His Highness's belongings.

01:56.336 --> 01:59.152
(To Mo Jingli at Lishan Academy)

01:59.504 --> 02:03.696
(Prince Ding's Mansion)

02:05.464 --> 02:07.024
- Your Highness.
- Where's the Princess Consort?

02:07.225 --> 02:09.185
She's in her chambers, Your Highness.

02:09.424 --> 02:10.065
Okay.

02:11.905 --> 02:15.424
Your Highness,
I noticed a strange matter.

02:15.704 --> 02:16.505
What is it?

02:17.065 --> 02:21.424
Now, the first thing you do upon returning
to the mansion is go find Her Highness.

02:22.864 --> 02:23.864
Is this strange?

02:28.264 --> 02:32.144
Your Highness, the person
over there seems to be Lady Su.

02:58.185 --> 03:01.584
Been away so long, I forgot that
Dachu nights are damp and cold.

03:01.905 --> 03:04.424
So I caught a cold carelessly.

03:11.065 --> 03:14.424
I remember when I visited
the mansion as a child,

03:14.905 --> 03:17.505
there was a twin-trunked tree here.

03:17.984 --> 03:20.625
Why is there only one trunk
remaining now?

03:21.824 --> 03:24.264
No idea. Perhaps it withered and died.

03:29.584 --> 03:30.905
After all,

03:32.584 --> 03:33.864
nothing lasts forever.

03:39.104 --> 03:41.745
Last night, I happened upon Ms. Wen.

03:42.065 --> 03:44.785
Coming here rashly
was really not my intention.

03:45.945 --> 03:51.544
Actually, given my current status,
I really shouldn't meet you again.

03:53.144 --> 03:57.065
I saw Princess Consort yesterday.
She is indeed elegant and steady.

04:06.704 --> 04:10.225
I heard she hails from Lishan Mountain.
Must be extraordinary.

04:11.185 --> 04:15.544
You have suffered a lot over the years,
having a tough time.

04:16.464 --> 04:19.264
Now, seeing you're doing well

04:19.745 --> 04:21.704
and having a happy marriage
with Princess Consort,

04:22.185 --> 04:25.425
I feel very relieved.

04:31.344 --> 04:32.945
You serve Princess Lingyun.

04:33.344 --> 04:36.065
Can you be absent all night like this?

04:36.985 --> 04:38.344
Thank you for your concern.

04:39.185 --> 04:42.144
Ms. Wen has already sent word
to the posthouse,

04:43.105 --> 04:48.105
saying I happened to run into
old acquaintances and took some days off.

05:05.464 --> 05:09.105
I... I've been out too long.
Ms. Wen must be looking for me.

05:09.665 --> 05:12.425
Your Highness, I shall take my leave.

05:29.104 --> 05:31.696
(To Mo Jingli at Lishan Academy)

05:42.784 --> 05:45.545
Li, how was your day?

05:46.945 --> 05:49.264
I checked on the shop. All is well.

05:53.384 --> 05:55.425
Your Highnesses, it is time to dine.

05:55.745 --> 05:57.105
Let's go eat.

06:03.536 --> 06:09.328
(Prison)

06:16.425 --> 06:20.264
Now you're at this state,
yet you still plan to hold on?

06:21.344 --> 06:23.305
This is nothing but a frame-up!

06:24.625 --> 06:31.088
The Cangbei rebels want to sow discord
between the Dachu court and its ministers!

06:35.185 --> 06:38.625
It's okay. You will talk one day.

06:46.545 --> 06:50.185
Prince Ding! This is a frame-up!

06:51.305 --> 06:57.105
I demand to see Marquis Muyang!

07:05.812 --> 07:10.384
(Marquis Muyang's Mansion)

07:10.985 --> 07:12.344
That day, it all started suddenly.

07:12.464 --> 07:15.065
We had to deploy our agents
within the palace to surround him.

07:15.384 --> 07:17.680
But I never expected
Prince Ding's legs had healed.

07:17.680 --> 07:19.024
It's my fault.

07:19.024 --> 07:19.704
Enough!

07:20.745 --> 07:23.625
The die is cast.
What's the point of saying all this?

07:55.144 --> 07:56.745
I am not blaming you.

07:57.745 --> 07:59.425
Mo Xiuyao is extremely cunning.

08:01.065 --> 08:04.545
Even I was deceived by him,
let alone you.

08:06.784 --> 08:09.185
But the current situation is perilous.

08:10.224 --> 08:12.264
Zhang Hengyuan is not tough.

08:13.065 --> 08:15.344
He won't hold out long
under Mo Xiuyao's interrogation.

08:16.185 --> 08:19.985
If he talks, we are all doomed.

08:21.425 --> 08:22.784
What do you expect me to do?

08:25.224 --> 08:28.904
Infiltrate the Jingzhao Prefecture prison
and silence him.

08:33.224 --> 08:34.945
It is heavily guarded. I'm afraid...

08:34.945 --> 08:35.905
It's the only way.

08:40.104 --> 08:40.744
Rest assured.

08:41.945 --> 08:45.785
I've already
arranged everything for you.

08:46.025 --> 08:48.224
Once it is done,
you'll depart immediately

08:49.104 --> 08:50.704
to Yunchuan to lie low.

08:51.744 --> 08:54.425
I have already arranged a new identity,

08:55.265 --> 08:57.305
manors, lands, and assets for you.

08:58.624 --> 09:00.025
Once everything's passed,

09:01.344 --> 09:06.545
I shall bring you back as my adopted son
to the capital openly and honorably.

09:10.824 --> 09:11.624
Adopted son?

09:13.584 --> 09:14.385
Yes.

09:17.185 --> 09:21.385
All these years,
though I never voiced it,

09:22.744 --> 09:27.385
I've been thinking of you in my mind.

09:30.464 --> 09:34.785
You are my own son,
connected by bloodline.

09:35.704 --> 09:38.344
How could I bear
to see you live far away alone,

09:38.545 --> 09:40.065
without returning to your clan?

09:43.744 --> 09:44.864
I swear,

09:45.905 --> 09:47.344
when you return from Yunchuan,

09:48.784 --> 09:51.305
you won't do those
dangerous tasks again.

09:53.984 --> 09:55.824
But given the current situation,

09:57.624 --> 10:02.824
I can trust no one but you.

10:11.216 --> 10:12.432
Rest assured, Marquis Muyang.

10:14.145 --> 10:15.704
I will kill Zhang Hengyuan.

10:21.744 --> 10:26.265
Do you still address me
as Marquis Muyang?

10:43.145 --> 10:46.504
Be cautious.
I'm waiting for your return.

10:51.104 --> 10:51.945
Yes.

10:58.104 --> 10:58.905
Zhao Ting.

11:01.704 --> 11:02.504
Marquis Muyang.

11:03.425 --> 11:04.224
Follow him.

11:04.545 --> 11:07.385
If any mistake occurs, spare no one.

11:07.624 --> 11:08.385
Yes.

11:15.305 --> 11:16.104
Father.

11:17.864 --> 11:19.704
What truly happened
at the palace that day?

11:20.025 --> 11:21.624
Does it have anything to do with us?

11:21.905 --> 11:24.265
Did Zhang Hengyuan get arrested
because of his corruption?

11:24.624 --> 11:26.744
And you were left behind.

11:26.744 --> 11:29.185
Did the Emperor and Empress Dowager
give you a hard time?

11:29.624 --> 11:31.744
Alright, stop asking questions.

11:33.185 --> 11:35.584
You sent Qin Cang to silence
someone. I can do that too.

11:35.584 --> 11:36.104
Want me to...

11:36.104 --> 11:36.785
Enough nonsense!

11:37.624 --> 11:39.984
Don't get your hands dirty
with bloodshed.

11:41.425 --> 11:42.145
Why?

11:42.145 --> 11:44.545
No why. I said no, so it's no.

11:48.344 --> 11:49.905
You just said to spare no one.

11:52.464 --> 11:54.624
Do you mean to kill Qin Cang as well?

11:56.464 --> 11:57.385
Father.

11:58.864 --> 12:00.185
He is your son.

12:10.584 --> 12:15.824
Remember, you are my only son.

12:35.984 --> 12:38.288
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

13:40.665 --> 13:42.305
Fire! Hurry! Fire!

13:42.824 --> 13:43.856
Fire!

13:43.856 --> 13:45.864
Attention! Fire!

13:46.448 --> 13:47.952
Hurry! Go put out the fire!

13:47.952 --> 13:49.567
You lot, go fetch water!

14:01.025 --> 14:03.408
Fire! Hurry!

14:14.785 --> 14:17.744
Qin Cang, you're here to rescue me
on Marquis Muyang's orders, right?

14:17.984 --> 14:20.624
Come on, open the cell now! Let me out!

14:20.665 --> 14:22.285
Come on!

14:28.545 --> 14:31.464
Wait, you're not here to rescue me.

14:32.104 --> 14:34.545
Marquis Muyang sent you to silence me.

14:36.584 --> 14:37.824
I didn't say anything.

14:47.905 --> 14:51.104
Marquis Muyang, why?

14:57.984 --> 14:58.864
Who's there?

14:59.584 --> 15:01.145
Help! Murder!

15:12.984 --> 15:14.545
He is over there! Capture him!

16:11.945 --> 16:12.744
Who's there?

16:16.824 --> 16:18.265
Marquis Muyang sent me to help you.

16:25.305 --> 16:26.385
How did it go?

16:27.185 --> 16:28.344
You killed Zhang Hengyuan?

16:33.145 --> 16:33.945
Qin Cang!

16:35.785 --> 16:37.665
He's here to kill you. Run!

16:48.665 --> 16:49.665
Qin Cang.

16:55.785 --> 16:56.905
Qin Cang!

16:57.744 --> 16:59.744
Qin Cang!

17:11.425 --> 17:13.865
They couldn't have gone far.
They must be nearby.

17:18.865 --> 17:20.064
Spread out and search.

17:24.585 --> 17:25.585
That way.

17:27.224 --> 17:28.385
Check inside.

17:42.032 --> 17:45.376
(Marquis Muyang's Mansion)

17:52.945 --> 17:55.024
Marquis Muyang, Zhang Hengyuan is dead.

17:55.105 --> 17:57.665
Qin Cang was exposed,
so I've dealt with...

18:23.504 --> 18:25.145
You summoned me early this morning.

18:25.425 --> 18:27.440
You must've anticipated
that Marquis Muyang

18:27.440 --> 18:30.064
would be coming today
to seek your forgiveness again.

18:31.984 --> 18:35.784
Over these years, every time
he messes up, he puts on the same show.

18:37.825 --> 18:38.984
I am weary.

18:40.224 --> 18:44.425
The one who died in Jingzhao Prefecture
last night was truly his own son?

18:46.625 --> 18:48.264
Even tigers don't eat their own young.

18:48.984 --> 18:51.145
Marquis Muyang is beyond redemption.

18:53.185 --> 18:56.185
What benefits could he obtain
from doing this?

19:02.704 --> 19:05.984
I taught you before.
Attack the enemy, but watch yourself.

19:06.544 --> 19:08.544
Marquis Muyang never grasps it.

19:09.625 --> 19:11.945
Look at you. You're the same.

19:12.784 --> 19:15.425
Well, you've never let me win once.

19:18.145 --> 19:21.744
Marquis Muyang.
Let me announce it first.

19:22.425 --> 19:23.345
Marquis Muyang!

19:24.024 --> 19:25.464
It is just as you anticipated.

19:27.704 --> 19:28.865
All of you, withdraw.

19:29.224 --> 19:31.120
Marquis Muyang,
let me announce it first.

19:31.120 --> 19:31.952
Marquis Muyang...

19:34.425 --> 19:38.024
Your Majesty, I'm here
to seek your forgiveness.

19:38.945 --> 19:40.784
Marquis Muyang, why seek my forgiveness?

19:41.585 --> 19:45.224
What happened at Jingzhao Prefecture
last night was my doing.

19:49.105 --> 19:53.264
You're so eager to silence Zhang Hengyuan,
even asking your own son to do this.

19:54.625 --> 19:57.145
It seems the secrets Zhang Hengyuan knew

19:57.784 --> 20:00.105
were potent enough
to shake your foundations.

20:03.464 --> 20:06.825
Is his collusion with Cangbei
related to you?

20:07.625 --> 20:08.704
Absolutely not.

20:10.185 --> 20:13.544
Everything I have done is for you.

20:13.784 --> 20:16.105
Marquis Muyang, mind your words.

20:23.784 --> 20:27.304
Zhang Hengyuan and Lu Changfu
followed me for many years.

20:27.345 --> 20:32.145
You know well how many
tasks they handled for me.

20:33.224 --> 20:36.844
If I weren't afraid that Zhang Hengyuan
might blab nonsense in prison,

20:36.844 --> 20:40.464
bringing up the past deeds
that would damage your reputation,

20:42.024 --> 20:44.544
I would never have resorted
to such an extreme measure.

20:45.224 --> 20:51.504
Over these years, for you and the nation,
I've made countless enemies

20:51.945 --> 20:53.264
and few to trust.

20:53.784 --> 20:56.905
Now, villains are taking them out.

20:57.544 --> 21:00.865
Until last night, even my own son

21:02.024 --> 21:03.504
could not escape.

21:07.024 --> 21:10.105
In that case, Marquis Muyang,
accept our condolences.

21:10.825 --> 21:13.224
Let bygones be bygones.

21:16.304 --> 21:17.145
Bygones?

21:19.905 --> 21:21.024
Can they be?

21:23.145 --> 21:24.625
You may have forgotten that

21:25.464 --> 21:27.064
Qin Cang's original surname was Zhou.

21:28.625 --> 21:29.784
He was called Zhou Lang.

21:30.105 --> 21:34.024
His birth mother was the daughter
of an Eastern Palace attendant.

21:35.304 --> 21:37.145
I was afraid it would worry you,

21:39.024 --> 21:41.905
so I hid his true origins
for many years.

21:42.625 --> 21:47.625
Because I've always seen you
as the real sovereign.

21:48.585 --> 21:52.385
I want to serve you with everything I have.
So I married the Kang woman.

21:52.464 --> 21:53.185
Shut up!

21:58.345 --> 22:01.345
What's the point of
your telling me all this now?

22:02.224 --> 22:04.224
If you truly care for that child,

22:04.704 --> 22:07.945
why did you send him
to do those shady things for you?

22:08.425 --> 22:10.385
And why did you send
assassins to silence him?

22:11.704 --> 22:14.825
Eight years have passed. Prince Ding
has grown more composed,

22:15.145 --> 22:19.984
yet you grow increasingly arrogant,
blinded by desires and ambitions.

22:19.984 --> 22:20.865
How foolish!

22:27.264 --> 22:28.744
I am foolish?

22:31.905 --> 22:35.585
I have spared no effort
and devoted my all.

22:37.264 --> 22:40.945
Everything I've done is for you,

22:42.185 --> 22:43.984
and Dachu, isn't it?

22:45.185 --> 22:47.784
The wise mend their deficiencies.

22:48.185 --> 22:50.224
The foolish offer others
their weaknesses.

22:50.784 --> 22:52.064
Time has changed.

22:52.704 --> 22:56.544
Marquis Muyang, you should
learn to move with the times.

23:06.224 --> 23:11.856
Your Majesty dwells high above,
holding up the heavens.

23:11.856 --> 23:13.544
Naturally, your hands remain spotless.

23:14.264 --> 23:15.625
But what about my hands?

23:17.425 --> 23:21.264
My hands are stained with filth,
marked with blood,

23:21.385 --> 23:23.385
and burdened
by all those deeds from the past.

23:24.425 --> 23:26.945
And now, you expect a mere
"let bygones be bygones"

23:27.345 --> 23:29.945
to wipe it all away?

23:31.825 --> 23:35.185
Marquis Muyang, never forget that

23:35.704 --> 23:39.464
every step you took
was a calculated move.

23:40.185 --> 23:43.544
You reached out your hand
not out of loyalty,

23:43.825 --> 23:46.665
but because you saw the 'price tag'
and thought it was worth it.

23:47.425 --> 23:53.264
Now, there's no need for you
to play a loyal man before me.

24:07.664 --> 24:09.840
(Linjiao Courtyard)

24:11.105 --> 24:14.385
You are such a busy soul,
always rejecting invitations.

24:14.905 --> 24:19.304
What brought you here
into my quiet courtyard today?

24:21.544 --> 24:25.625
An old friend returned from Lingnan
and brought me this box of Tuoluo cakes.

24:34.665 --> 24:36.304
I heard you hail from Lingnan.

24:36.625 --> 24:39.304
I thought you might crave this taste.

24:39.784 --> 24:42.744
So I brought them to you,
hoping to bring you some pleasure.

24:49.744 --> 24:51.425
How thoughtful.

24:54.024 --> 24:57.024
Indeed, it stirs my homesickness.

25:03.865 --> 25:06.625
You seem troubled today.

25:12.345 --> 25:15.585
What do you think of Marquis Muyang?

25:21.464 --> 25:26.224
Since you ask,
I will speak frankly then.

25:28.224 --> 25:31.504
Marquis Muyang possesses
only an arrogant demeanor,

25:32.105 --> 25:33.544
yet lacks true talent.

25:33.984 --> 25:36.105
Stubbornness leads to betrayal.

25:36.464 --> 25:38.345
Narrow-mindedness
brings one to a dead end.

25:38.665 --> 25:42.585
He is nothing but rotting bones
in a tomb, bound for a swift end.

25:44.865 --> 25:46.544
"Rotting bones in a tomb."

25:47.344 --> 25:48.688
The most intricate webs of deceit

25:48.688 --> 25:53.704
are entirely transparent
to your eyes, clear as water.

25:54.264 --> 25:56.145
No wonder the Empress Dowager
favors you so.

25:57.385 --> 26:02.345
Turns out I'm the idiot here,
still clinging to the ghost of the past.

26:02.784 --> 26:05.264
Surely that is not the case,
Your Highness.

26:05.585 --> 26:08.145
I am merely an outsider.

26:08.625 --> 26:11.304
I said that only by observing
the game as an outsider.

26:11.825 --> 26:14.744
Forgive any offense, Your Highness.

26:38.544 --> 26:40.304
The Su family isn't
completely wiped out.

26:40.984 --> 26:44.865
Her eldest brother, Su Huaizhong,
now trades silk in Huaizhou,

26:45.105 --> 26:47.744
specializing in fine silk
from Song and Bo prefectures.

26:48.185 --> 26:50.945
They say this year, he's taken
orders from a Persian caravan.

26:51.544 --> 26:54.145
And her younger sister, Su Zuichan,
married a ninth-rank clerk

26:54.145 --> 26:56.145
from Jingzhao Prefecture's
Bureau of Revenue,

26:56.385 --> 27:00.185
who manages household registries
and land disputes in the west of the capital.

27:00.544 --> 27:03.248
And her mom's dowry nanny, Ms. Wu,

27:04.080 --> 27:07.504
is now a chef at Xiangyun Tower.

27:07.504 --> 27:11.105
The Golden Thread Pastry
you praised last time is made by her.

27:13.425 --> 27:15.625
Got it. Thank you, Senior Wei.

27:40.345 --> 27:41.425
What are you doing?

27:42.704 --> 27:43.544
Working.

27:45.264 --> 27:47.185
You're rubbing that table raw.

27:48.064 --> 27:50.865
Planning to stay forever, are you?

27:51.704 --> 27:53.504
I'm not in your way.

27:56.105 --> 27:58.905
As an assassin, you work here.

27:58.984 --> 27:59.905
Where's your ambition?

28:02.345 --> 28:03.224
None of your business.

28:06.625 --> 28:07.856
Is Princess Ding here?

28:07.856 --> 28:09.109
There.

28:11.744 --> 28:14.064
Your Highness, something's
happened to Yusheng.

28:24.464 --> 28:25.544
Princess Ding isn't back?

28:26.865 --> 28:28.784
Not yet, Your Highness.

28:30.625 --> 28:31.665
Any message?

28:32.905 --> 28:34.744
N-No.

28:52.048 --> 28:54.064
(To Mo Jingli at Lishan Academy)

29:13.385 --> 29:17.105
Thank you, Your Highness.
I didn't expect you to come.

29:17.425 --> 29:19.024
You're someone my senior favors.

29:19.224 --> 29:21.385
If you're in trouble,
I won't stand idly by.

29:23.504 --> 29:24.665
You are so kind.

29:25.905 --> 29:27.665
No wonder you'd care
for someone like me.

29:29.464 --> 29:32.464
He's my patron, and I'm his confidant.

29:33.064 --> 29:34.744
Everyone here knows one rule.

29:35.105 --> 29:37.865
In a place like this,
never take anything to heart.

29:38.784 --> 29:42.625
Especially those impossible
and unreachable things.

29:50.905 --> 29:53.105
Do you agree, Young Master?

29:59.264 --> 30:01.625
You seem fine. I'll take my leave.

30:01.865 --> 30:02.945
Take care.

30:03.665 --> 30:07.024
If he comes to you again,
send word to me at Shende Shop.

30:10.105 --> 30:11.224
Thank you, Your Highness.

30:17.464 --> 30:18.665
What she said wasn't right.

30:20.185 --> 30:21.064
What do you mean?

30:21.544 --> 30:24.024
If you make up your mind,
you must go do it.

30:24.385 --> 30:26.905
How can you know if it's possible
without giving it a try?

30:29.064 --> 30:29.704
Your Highness.

30:33.145 --> 30:35.385
Your Highness, we've finally found you.

30:35.385 --> 30:36.464
Why are you here?

30:38.185 --> 30:40.665
You haven't returned this late.
His Highness is so worried.

30:40.744 --> 30:42.825
Everyone available
has been out to look for you.

30:43.145 --> 30:44.385
Please come back with me.

30:50.825 --> 30:51.585
Everyone, leave.

30:52.464 --> 30:53.345
- Yes.
- Yes.

31:04.425 --> 31:05.145
Say it.

31:08.024 --> 31:08.984
What?

31:11.064 --> 31:11.984
Where did you go?

31:13.585 --> 31:16.784
I... went to fight.

31:20.464 --> 31:22.544
Where? Why?

31:24.264 --> 31:25.385
A brothel.

31:26.105 --> 31:28.865
You? A brothel?

31:30.385 --> 31:33.145
I went back as soon as I finished there.

31:35.504 --> 31:36.304
Ye Li.

31:38.064 --> 31:39.425
I really don't understand you.

31:40.984 --> 31:43.464
You're always going somewhere
I can't place,

31:44.345 --> 31:46.264
doing something
I can't quite figure out.

31:46.945 --> 31:49.224
Do you even know who you are?

31:50.304 --> 31:53.865
Do you know that a woman walking alone
at night could be dangerous?

31:54.464 --> 31:58.825
Do you know how it feels waiting for you
at the mansion without any news?

32:02.665 --> 32:04.224
You fought in a brothel?

32:05.385 --> 32:06.264
With whom?

32:06.504 --> 32:09.224
What if you encountered desperadoes?
What if an accident happened?

32:10.704 --> 32:12.345
I didn't encounter desperadoes.

32:12.345 --> 32:13.105
Ye Li!

32:19.024 --> 32:22.224
I thought after all this time together,
you'd understand me.

32:24.224 --> 32:26.145
I thought you felt the same about me.

32:27.704 --> 32:28.585
But you...

32:35.264 --> 32:38.665
Have you ever taken
our marriage seriously?

32:52.665 --> 32:54.544
Perhaps we don't know
each other well enough.

32:54.544 --> 32:55.385
We do.

32:56.625 --> 32:57.425
What?

33:00.905 --> 33:02.185
We know each other.

33:03.984 --> 33:06.304
I know you've never given up
on yourself all these years.

33:08.825 --> 33:10.825
I know you cannot bear
the injustice forced upon

33:10.825 --> 33:12.464
Prince Ding's Mansion
and Heiyun Cavalry.

33:14.024 --> 33:17.784
I know you seek to reopen the case
and destroy Marquis Muyang.

33:19.665 --> 33:20.304
And I know

33:21.825 --> 33:23.105
you understand me.

33:32.224 --> 33:33.105
You know

33:34.825 --> 33:37.304
I'm not a woman who's willing
to be trapped in the mansion.

33:39.625 --> 33:41.665
You know I came down
the mountain for some reason.

33:43.585 --> 33:49.145
You know I'm related to the deaths
of Lv Cheng and Lu Changfu.

33:52.304 --> 33:53.345
And you know

33:54.784 --> 33:56.064
I have liked you

33:57.304 --> 33:59.064
for a long time.

34:05.905 --> 34:08.144
I won't do it again.

34:10.064 --> 34:11.745
I'm sorry for making you worry.

34:12.848 --> 34:16.848
ظآزDeepest love is none other thanظآز

34:16.848 --> 34:18.704
ظآزAligning my scars with yoursظآز

34:18.704 --> 34:20.315
ظآزWhat was once let goظآز

34:20.315 --> 34:22.337
ظآزWill heal together from now onظآز

34:22.337 --> 34:23.994
ظآزFrom your silhouetteظآز

34:23.994 --> 34:27.585
ظآزI see the same meظآز

34:27.585 --> 34:30.928
ظآزIf dreams become illusionsظآز

34:30.928 --> 34:33.584
ظآزWith you I journey and find solaceظآز

34:33.584 --> 34:35.163
ظآزIn the sole abode of heartظآز

34:35.163 --> 34:37.152
ظآزWe embrace and circle into a cornerظآز

34:37.152 --> 34:38.989
ظآزAmong worldly entanglementsظآز

34:38.989 --> 34:43.351
ظآزLove lightly brushes pastظآز

34:44.272 --> 34:46.284
ظآزLike you, like meظآز

34:46.638 --> 34:49.404
ظآزThe eyes are still clearظآز

34:51.472 --> 34:53.562
ظآزNone better than you,
and none better than meظآز

34:54.032 --> 34:55.785
ظآزLove can last until the springظآز

34:55.785 --> 34:56.984
Li.

35:02.024 --> 35:03.225
Li.

35:08.385 --> 35:09.385
Did you have a nightmare?

35:17.865 --> 35:19.945
I dreamed that I was all alone,

35:21.265 --> 35:23.225
walking on a desolate road,

35:24.945 --> 35:26.425
with nothing around.

35:27.464 --> 35:28.624
It was pitch black.

35:30.584 --> 35:32.785
It's okay. It was just a dream.

35:42.664 --> 35:44.785
I often have dreams like that.

35:46.425 --> 35:48.464
I'm scared every time I wake up.

35:49.184 --> 35:50.064
I'm here.

35:51.865 --> 35:53.984
I won't let you be alone again.

35:55.265 --> 35:56.144
Really?

35:59.865 --> 36:00.664
I promise,

36:02.425 --> 36:04.024
no matter what happens,

36:05.024 --> 36:08.464
I won't abandon you or leave you alone.

36:10.024 --> 36:11.785
In life and death, we shall not part.

36:12.664 --> 36:14.225
In weal and woe, we shall be one.

36:15.020 --> 36:18.256
ظآزAmidst life's ups and downs,
turns and twistsظآز

36:18.256 --> 36:22.096
ظآزLove has never strayed awayظآز

36:22.504 --> 36:24.305
I trust you.

36:24.944 --> 36:29.388
ظآزIn the end, we're together againظآز

36:29.840 --> 36:32.912
ظآزCountless trials and pleadings,
right or wrongظآز

36:32.912 --> 36:37.488
ظآزTry to make this love quietظآز

36:38.032 --> 36:39.724
ظآزBut we fight backظآز

36:39.724 --> 36:43.504
ظآزTo make it a tale to be toldظآز

36:47.280 --> 36:50.864
ظآزSilently, we turn pain into joyظآز

36:50.864 --> 36:52.286
ظآزYou reach out and pull meظآز

36:52.286 --> 36:54.480
ظآزAnd I gently touchظآز

36:54.480 --> 36:55.824
ظآزSmooth out the creasesظآز

36:55.824 --> 36:59.600
ظآزSo we can tightly fit togetherظآز

36:59.600 --> 37:02.576
ظآزWithout you, there's no meظآز

37:02.704 --> 37:05.328
ظآزPassing by the worldظآز

37:05.328 --> 37:06.768
ظآزPart of my broken selfظآز

37:06.768 --> 37:09.008
ظآزFinds our places in an embraceظآز

37:09.008 --> 37:10.704
ظآزFulfilling our wishesظآز

37:10.864 --> 37:15.408
ظآزLovers remain calm and composedظآز

37:16.112 --> 37:18.192
ظآزLike you, like meظآز

37:18.448 --> 37:21.456
ظآزIt's like a fond dreamظآز

37:23.728 --> 37:25.740
ظآزNone better than you,
and none better than meظآز

37:26.094 --> 37:34.027
ظآزLove blooms at every spring and sunsetظآز

37:53.648 --> 37:56.080
(I'm heading to Shende Shop)

37:56.265 --> 37:57.064
Fun, right?

37:57.305 --> 37:58.104
Yes.

37:58.984 --> 37:59.785
Are you feeling hot?

38:00.144 --> 38:00.945
Yes.

38:20.104 --> 38:23.345
(The intense heat from that day
was exactly the same as right now.)

38:24.584 --> 38:28.265
(The stone blocks along the street
seemed to be melting under the sun.)

38:28.945 --> 38:31.064
(The cicadas drone louder and faster,)

38:31.584 --> 38:34.624
(so piercing as if they might
split the very heavens.)

38:34.624 --> 38:35.624
It's so hot.

38:36.504 --> 38:38.984
My lady, it is really hot.

38:39.584 --> 38:40.664
Everything's prepared?

38:49.064 --> 38:52.584
(After Mo Xiuyao saved me,
I returned to the capital with Mom.)

38:53.664 --> 38:58.544
(For somehow, after we parted,
I often dreamt of him.)

38:59.945 --> 39:03.345
(Qingshuang said I had fallen for him.)

39:04.305 --> 39:07.785
(I didn't fully understand,
so I wanted to see him once again.)

39:09.624 --> 39:12.624
(I heard he went to serve Duke Hua.)

39:13.328 --> 39:16.624
(It so happened that Duke Hua returned
to the capital for his mother's birthday.)

39:17.624 --> 39:19.945
(As a personal guard,
he would travel along.)

39:21.024 --> 39:24.144
(I wanted to see him,
but didn't dare tell Mom.)

39:24.705 --> 39:28.544
(So I hired an escort carriage secretly
and took a rough ride out of the city.)

39:31.184 --> 39:34.984
(Duke Hua's forces were stationed at
Changding Camp, west of the capital.)

39:35.984 --> 39:37.984
(Changding isn't too far
from the capital.)

39:38.320 --> 39:39.536
- (Riding there)
- How about it?

39:39.536 --> 39:41.984
- (would only take about two hours.)
- The road was blocked.

39:43.504 --> 39:45.144
(But luck wasn't on my side.)

39:45.664 --> 39:48.624
- (A recent storm had washed away the roads,)
- Let's go.

39:48.624 --> 39:50.144
(blocking all carriages.)

39:50.624 --> 39:52.184
(So I had to take a small path.)

40:10.865 --> 40:12.305
(The heat was dizzying.)

40:13.385 --> 40:15.248
(The fruit drink in my small gourd)

40:15.248 --> 40:16.944
- (was running dry.)
- Drink it, My Lady.

40:18.225 --> 40:20.024
(My throat was still
parched and burning.)

40:20.664 --> 40:23.705
(My legs felt like lead,
making it hard to take another step.)

40:25.024 --> 40:27.534
- (Yet a fire burned in my chest,)
- Let's go.

40:27.534 --> 40:29.360
- (pushing me to move forward.)
- Go.

40:31.984 --> 40:35.024
(I had a question.
I had to ask him in person.)

40:41.664 --> 40:43.705
(Maybe my information was wrong.)

40:44.144 --> 40:46.584
(When I arrived, they'd already left.)

40:47.144 --> 40:48.544
(I didn't get to see him.)

40:58.905 --> 40:59.945
(Looking back,)

41:00.265 --> 41:04.745
(the small road from the capital to Changding
takes a mere four to six hours.)

41:06.104 --> 41:10.544
(Yet in my memory of that summer,
that road stretched on forever.)

41:11.624 --> 41:14.825
(The cicadas' chattering was deafening.)

41:54.144 --> 41:56.705
Can I ask you a question?

41:57.184 --> 41:57.984
Go ahead.

41:58.865 --> 42:02.448
The day we first met,
there were so many people there.

42:02.928 --> 42:05.504
Why did you just pull me
onto your saddle?

42:06.745 --> 42:08.144
Did you like me back then?

42:11.305 --> 42:14.584
You were about this tall.

42:15.705 --> 42:17.504
Your face got wet with snot and tears.

42:18.345 --> 42:19.385
What did I like about you?

42:20.905 --> 42:22.265
No snot!

42:26.504 --> 42:28.984
Your Highnesses,
what are you doing here?

42:29.104 --> 42:30.664
Waiting for you to open the shop.

42:32.265 --> 42:33.425
Please, come in.

42:39.408 --> 42:42.160
(Preview)

42:42.385 --> 42:43.624
We did have an engagement.

42:44.225 --> 42:48.225
But we were just kids back then.
Barely even knew each other.

42:48.905 --> 42:51.544
Things changed later, and we lost touch.

42:52.705 --> 42:56.984
If one day, I am in your way,
would you kill me then?

42:57.825 --> 43:00.184
Yao, let's make a bet.

43:00.865 --> 43:04.624
I bet the sun vanishes tomorrow,
right at the Wu hour.

43:15.736 --> 43:22.328
ظآزMemories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreamsظآز

43:25.912 --> 43:32.056
ظآزOnly by moving forward
can you find reunionظآز

43:34.264 --> 43:37.496
ظآزEndings only mark new routesظآز

43:37.720 --> 43:43.736
ظآزIt's all part of the sceneryظآز

43:44.056 --> 43:47.480
ظآزTo the horizon's callظآز

43:47.544 --> 43:54.104
ظآزYour journey hasn't startedظآز

43:55.160 --> 43:59.096
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

43:59.096 --> 44:04.792
ظآزBoth joy and grief
make the trip worthwhileظآز

44:05.304 --> 44:13.912
ظآزTrying to catch up
to your own lost shadowظآز

44:14.808 --> 44:20.312
ظآزWithin the wilds, echoes thriveظآز

44:20.312 --> 44:25.816
ظآزClear mind leads to a clear pathظآز

44:25.880 --> 44:29.944
ظآزBe grateful to your lossesظآز

44:30.232 --> 44:35.456
ظآزMake your steps weightlessظآز

44:36.056 --> 44:39.768
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

44:39.800 --> 44:45.464
ظآزLet time embrace you
and wash away the pastظآز

44:46.232 --> 44:54.200
ظآزPut every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through timeظآز

44:55.608 --> 45:00.856
ظآزMake headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your paceظآز

45:01.112 --> 45:07.016
ظآزRush towards a life without regretظآز

45:07.016 --> 45:11.136
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

45:11.352 --> 45:16.088
ظآزUnbound by formظآز

45:17.304 --> 45:21.576
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

45:21.816 --> 45:27.256
ظآزUnbound by formظآز
